settings.description: The 'Ultimate" airship is hare! You must board it and get through it, then fight Boom Boom, the airship creator! Don't die or you will be forced to restart, he is a lot harder this time!
Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...
You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV
Mario finds himself in a World with water, can he escape to cloud land? Base of operations of M and L are ahead, so be quick!
Mario Adventures Through the clouds to get to Bowsers Castle, nowhere near yet...
Roto-discs are like Fire Bars, but with much more room to dodge! Just make sure to keep your wits about you; they're a lot faster, too!
You find yourself in an unknown dimension, and you must find your ship. Will you escape, or will you stay here forever?
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.

Welcome to the Museum! Come gawk at some of the strange critters that are native to the Mushroom Kingdom!
Difficulty: 1/5

Hit the switches! But where's that dang 3rd Ace Coin!?
Difficulty: 3.5/5
